```mermaid
flowchart LR
    A([Trigger Event]) --> B{Workflow\nScheduler}
    B -->|Cron| C[Start Workflow]
    B -->|Manual| C
    C --> D[Load Config]
    D --> E[Initialize Agent]
    E --> F[Execute Tasks]
    F --> G{Task Type}

    G -->|Agent| H[LangGraph /\nCrewAI Agent]
    G -->|Email| I[Resend /\nAgentMail /\nBrevo]
    G -->|Notify| J[OneSignal /\nKnock]
    G -->|Blockchain| K[Monad RPC /\nSmart Contract]

    H --> L[Process with LLM]
    L --> M[Save Results]
    I --> M
    J --> M
    K --> M

    M --> N{Success?}
    N -->|Yes| O[Notify User]
    N -->|No| P[Retry Logic]
    P -->|Max Retries| Q[Alert Admin]
    P -->|< Max| G
    O --> R([End])

    style A fill:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    style R fill:#22c55e,color:#fff
    style P fill:#ef4444,color:#fff
```
